Category:Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope actors

nodes.text: Pam Rose (born August, 1947) is an English actress who portrayed Leesub Sirln, an alien in Chalmun's Spaceport Cantina in Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope
She is credited by John Mollo as portraying a 'weird girl' in Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope as documented in the 1979 book The Art of Star Wars.
